<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313721>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Zethus angulatus, 1, 2, 5, 6, male; 3, 4, female. 1, clypeus and mandibles; 2, mesosoma in dorsal view; 3, lateral habitus; 4, metasoma in dorsal view; 5, 6, antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313723>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–11. Zethus angulatus, female. 7, head in frontal view; 8, head in dorsal view; 9, propodeum in dorsal view; 10, tegula; 11, propodeum in lateral view. bf, basal fovea of propodeum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313723/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313735>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–33. Male genitalia of Zethus in ventral view. 32, Z. angulatus; 33, Z. bakeri. crv, volsellar ridge; cu, cupis; di, digitus; go, gonocoxite; lbd, basal lobe of digitus; ldd, distal lobe of digitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8313737>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34–39. Male genital structures of Zethus, 34, 36, 37, Z. angulatus; 35, 38, 39, Z. bakeri. 34 & 35, left volsella, inner view; 36 & 38, aedeagus in lateral view; 37 & 39, aedeagus in ventral view. ap, basal apodeme of aedeagus; lvv, ventral lobe of penis valve; pb, basal plate of aedeagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8313737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

